        <heading>956.  Claims of successor who is a creditor of the estate</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 956.  Claims of successor who is a creditor of the estate
A successor may assert a claim that he has as a creditor of the estate whether he accepts or renounces his succession rights.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
